	<Title>
		GERD: Can certain medications increase severity?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Certain medications can aggravate symptoms of gastroesophageal reflux disease (GERD). Learn more.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		I&apos;ve heard that some medications can aggravate the symptoms of GERD. Can you tell me more?
